#if soper
nickserv/set_nopassword
#endif
Help for SET NOPASSWORD:

SET NOPASSWORD prevents password-based authentication
attempts except for XMLRPC/JSONRPC. You will need to
be identified using a passwordless authentication
mechanism to be able to use NickServ GHOST, RELEASE
and REGAIN.

Syntax: SET NOPASSWORD ON|OFF

Example:
    /msg &nick& SET NOPASSWORD ON